              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
We say the <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Q]]></fr:tex>-convergence is of order <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(p \geq 1)]]></fr:tex> and with factor <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(\gamma  > 0)]]></fr:tex>, if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\exists  k_{0}]]></fr:tex>, such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\forall  k\geq  k_{0}]]></fr:tex>: <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\boxed {\min _{\mathbf {x_{*}}\in \mathcal {X}}||\mathbf {x_{k}}-\mathbf {x_{*}}||_{2}\ \leq \ \gamma \cdot \left (\min _{\mathbf {x_{*}}\in \mathcal {X}}||\mathbf {x_{k-1}}-\mathbf {x_{*}}||_{2}\right )^{p}.}]]></fr:tex></html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
